              <span class="st-cl-tag feat">feat</span>
              <p class="st-cl-text">Added EN/PL/IT language toggle to header nav (integrated, not floating) — auto-detect + localStorage persistence</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="st-cl-item">
            <span class="st-cl-date">2026-05</span>
            <div class="st-cl-body">
              <span class="st-cl-tag feat">feat</span>
              <p class="st-cl-text">Replaced 2-line footer with full 3-column grid: brand, Network, Connect — consistent with ecosystem</p>
